Go index by index
Take two choices at every index ->  best answer ending at this index and take choice
    - at each index i best answer ending at index i
    - for best answer add current index to prev ans(extend previous subarray) or discard all prev and keep current index(start afresh from current element)

pseudo code
    till last element
        v1 = prev res+ current index value
        v2= current index value

        currentBest = best(v1,v2)
        bestSoFar = best(currentBest,bestSoFar)
    return bestSoFar
